sentences.english: As a result, many of my comments will seem heretical to the high-level language purists out there.
sentences.chinese: 因此，我的許多意見將是被視爲高階語言的邪說。

sentences.english: In fact, AOP can be seen as a high level language for bytecode manipulation.
sentences.chinese: 實際上，AOP可以視作是操作字節碼的高階語言。

sentences.english: It is recommended that the students who study this course should study the High level programming lab course at the same time.
sentences.chinese: 初學者應同時修讀高階語言程式設計實習的課程。
